strings: <voice_0x0100174D><se_low>King Trode: It's been a long journey.

<voice_0x0100174E><se_low>King Trode: A lot has happened along the way,
but it's all worked out well in the end.
<voice_0x01001873><se_low>King Trode: How curious to think that you would have been Prince of Argonia had things been different.
<voice_0x01001874><se_low>King Trode: Fate deals strange hands indeed.
<voice_0x01001875><se_low>King Trode: Well... Pooh to those old promises made so many years ago!
<voice_0x01001876><se_low>King Trode: Now you two are free to decide your own destiny...

<voice_0x01001752><se_high>Princess Medea: Never mind that now, Father.
Look! We're home! Home for good!
